    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Directly instructing others in knowledge, attitudes, or skills. For the acquiring or imparting of specific skills relating to particular functions or activities through instruction or practice, use "training."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
